race.description: Irish Stallion Farms Ebf (C & G) Maiden
race.comment: EVENING BLUES (5) made a pleasing return when battling on gamely for second over 1408m at this track. That run could bring him forward again and may excel here to rate a major threat. GOLDEN TRIGGER (9) faces slightly easier opposition than on debut when a solid 1.75L third. Tackles the same trip here and with natural improvement shapes as a leading contender. MINELLA ROCKETT (11) resumed with a determined third over 1609m. Entitled to progress further and this looks an easier assignment. COEXIST (2) is a debutant by Soldier Hollow out of the proven producer Wamika. Must be monitored closely in the market.
